Dwell and Mean Current\
\
Reads an events list (.txt) and .abf file (saved as int) and outputs a csv with two columns, Mean Dwell time and Mean Current. Each row represents an event that was identified in the recording.\
\
INPUT:\
events list (.txt)\
.abf file (saved as int)\
\
OUTPUT:\
dwell_and_meanCurrent_1.csv\
