2DHistogram\
\
This script can be used to build dwell time(x axis) and mean current (y axis) histograms (z-axis) from any number of \'93dwell_and_meanCurrent.csv\'94 files. To analysis multiple files, add \'93_1\'94, \'93_2\'94, etc. to each file and move to same home folder as the script.\
The script asks for the range of x and y values, as well as the number of bins for each axis. The output file Dwell_and_Meancurrent_rebinned.csv\'94 can be used to make scatterplots or bubble plots.\
\
INPUT dwell_and_meanCurrent_1.csv and a range of values and # of bins for x and y.\
NOTE to analyze negative currents input the lowest value first (i.e -20,0) instead of (0,-20). \
\
OUTPUT\
Dwell_and_MeanCurrent_2DHist.csv\
